Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.08,0:00:08.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「風搖{\fn楷体\fscx83\fscy83}梄{\r}樹葉」呢 千早
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.76,0:00:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早 八百年前 詠唱「かぜそよぐ」的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.69,0:00:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是非常涼爽的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.28,0:00:43.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\an8}みそぎぞなつの  しるしなりける\N{\fs40}暮色清涼處 正值夏暑天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.88,0:00:48.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至能聽得見風聲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.76,0:00:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\an8}すみのえの  きしによるなみ  よるさへや\N{\fs40}浪湧住江岸 更深夜靜時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.32,0:00:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小奏 我記得
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.19,0:01:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到夢 就是「すみのえ」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.49,0:01:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惠夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.27,0:01:20.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好地決一勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.52,0:02:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前沒能搶到的敵陣右下段的一字決…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:48.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搶到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.91,0:02:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵陣中的一字決
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.00,0:02:58.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對誰來說都是很特別的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.31,0:03:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像是打了別人的臉一樣拿到牌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.65,0:03:03.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那讓人超開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:05.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,形勢會轉向千早
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:08.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的速度 果然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.34,0:03:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs38\fad(100,100)}參宿五
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.34,0:03:13.31,line,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fscx1800\fscy120\pos(4,68)\fad(100,100)}-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.34,0:03:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs38\an7\pos(100,60)\fad(100,100)}女戰士之星 對千早的稱呼 詳見第十話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.34,0:03:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「參宿五」的神經信號是由耳朵直通手指的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.70,0:03:15.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不是這樣就不可能用那種速度搶到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:22.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且敵陣左下段中發S音的一字決 明明有「せ」在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.56,0:03:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻攻向了「す」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.73,0:03:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多麼有勇氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.75,0:03:30.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.49,0:03:33.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漂亮地到達了…那個角落裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.45,0:03:37.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前一直無法做到的搶牌…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.92,0:03:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早 幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.89,0:03:40.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.10,0:03:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在想著「太好了」的瞬間 集中力就會分散
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.38,0:03:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36}わがいほは{\r}\N我住皇都外
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:49.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36}こころにも{\r}\N不愛紅塵誤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:56.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.32,0:03:59.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 惠夢 沒有受到影響
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.61,0:04:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自陣的一字決被搶走了 也沒有讓比賽朝壞的方向流轉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.97,0:04:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是西日本的代表
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明石女子的王牌兼氣氛營造者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.43,0:04:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逢坂惠夢的表現 關係到比賽的勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:20.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧 一張張的 加油上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.81,0:04:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣冷靜的選手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:27.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是第一次遇到…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.69,0:04:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\an8}こひしかるべき  よはのつきかな{\fs40}\N今宵何所戀 夜半月中天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:36.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走向 該如何掌握來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.53,0:04:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36}はるのよの{\r}\N恍惚春宵夢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.15,0:04:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同…同時
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.06,0:04:42.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要退縮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.07,0:04:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去爭！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…是我搶到的…吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.86,0:04:54.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是說一定要把這張牌變成自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.53,0:04:56.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算最後讓給對方了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.24,0:04:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要讓對方覺得「真是個麻煩的傢伙」就有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.31,0:05:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要打亂對方的步調
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.81,0:05:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是同時 所以剛剛的明明應該是惠夢的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:07.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.65,0:05:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 那麼 給你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.05,0:05:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變成了自己的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.85,0:05:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會 怎麼會 怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.89,0:05:16.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎 怎 怎 怎麼辦才好…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.32,0:05:17.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36}はるすぎて{\r}\N春盡夏已到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.95,0:05:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.03,0:05:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為被讓了牌 反而擾亂了自己的步調
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.10,0:05:24.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打從心底覺得她不適合去爭牌…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.29,0:05:26.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要努力才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.73,0:05:29.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要努力才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.92,0:05:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要努力…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.22,0:05:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:36.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的氛圍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的觀眾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體比想像中的更難以動彈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.16,0:05:43.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\an8}やまがはに {\fs40}\N濺濺山溪淌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空牌 好危險
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.15,0:05:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花野…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.09,0:05:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根據花野的筆記來看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:05:58.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紮馬尾的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:06:01.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛巾…蒼井龍二的旅遊毛巾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.18,0:06:04.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛巾 說的是那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.49,0:06:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真虧她竟然連這都知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.98,0:06:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到蒼井龍二
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.51,0:06:11.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是唱那種超甜蜜情歌的歌手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.92,0:06:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依依不捨的悲戀派
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:17.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.65,0:06:20.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這邊的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:23.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\an8}みちのくの{\fs40}\N紛紛心緒亂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.70,0:06:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搶下來！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.34,0:06:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我瞄準的牌給搶走了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:28.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說這個人是C級 可是真難對付
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天才第一次出場的我 要進入狀態才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.43,0:06:35.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守住了哦 接下來也要搶到哦 瑞澤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.47,0:06:36.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:41.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花野同學 觀察得很仔細
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.41,0:06:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:51.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\an8}おほえやま  いくののみちの  とほければ{\fs40}\N山長平野闊 母去路悠悠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:51.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「おおえ」 大家都搶到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.08,0:06:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比賽走向一定會轉向我們這邊 這次一定會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.23,0:06:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂的走向…所謂的走向
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:01.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是指的連取！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:04.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36}いまこむと{\r}\N夜夜盼君到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.43,0:07:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銅牆鐵壁一般的穩定感
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:13.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊搶到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係 先搶一張 一張張來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:20.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 抱歉 惠夢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這樣的大舞臺中也能如此氣定神閒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惠夢好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:28.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 就算是一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:30.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也還是不明白惠夢的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然大家興奮地說著「讓惠夢成為女王」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.06,0:07:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但惠夢真實的想法是怎樣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.33,0:07:40.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她…想成為女王嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.92,0:07:42.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早沒辦法連取
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.57,0:07:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差距在漸漸擴大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:49.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早 贏了就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:50.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要贏哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:53.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是又說過頭了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.86,0:07:58.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她跟去年不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經過了一年了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:05.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一年
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36}ありあけのつきを  まちいでつるかな{\r}\N相約定不忘 又待月西沉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.88,0:08:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\an8}あまつかぜ  くものかよひぢ  ふきとぢよ{\fs40}\N浩蕩天風起 雲中路莫開
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空牌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.04,0:08:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出手的時候很快 收回的時候也很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.62,0:08:35.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.65,0:08:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有被逢坂同學的快速出手影響到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:52.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:08:54.49,comments_h,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\frz350.8\c&H7C51D3&\move(696,196,706,184,22,1648)}惠{\c&HC38687&}夢 {\c&H7DB2F3&}加{\c&H69BA65&}油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.26,0:09:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深深的感受到了 青春啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.03,0:09:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭帶已經成為逢坂惠夢的標誌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.14,0:09:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然此前一直只有逢坂戴著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.66,0:09:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了全國大賽做的 大家一起帶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.41,0:09:17.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是為之前為我所做的回禮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.83,0:09:18.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惠夢學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.42,0:09:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太美好了 友情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.85,0:09:24.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能當歌牌部的顧問真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.41,0:09:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惠夢碳令我們喜歡的理由是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.79,0:09:31.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惠夢碳所擁有的巨大反差
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的鏡頭是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.28,0:09:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.85,0:09:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一個人戴頭帶實在太傻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.71,0:09:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能扯上大家一起戴太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.41,0:09:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36}をとめのすがた  しばしとどめむ{\r}\N仙姬留碧落 倩影暫徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.33,0:09:58.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36}あらざらむ{\r}\N般般身後事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.22,0:10:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從手的下面穿過去 被搶了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:07.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從一開始就一直被搶的「あ」牌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:09.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次這麼漂亮地搶到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.90,0:10:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是抓到什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.53,0:10:17.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.78,0:10:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 繼續 一張張地拿下來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.67,0:10:27.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.62,0:10:34.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是團體賽 為什麼只有我喊加油呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.60,0:10:37.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女王？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.27,0:10:39.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實那種事無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.14,0:10:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 要送牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.86,0:10:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 「あさぼらけう」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.19,0:10:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大山牌？ 為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.24,0:10:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般不會送這張牌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.20,0:11:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙應該不擅長大山牌的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.83,0:11:06.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是放棄那張了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.90,0:11:15.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36}いまひとたびの  あふこともがな{\r}\N漫漫黃泉路 也堪憶我胸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.82,0:11:21.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\an8}きみがため をしからざりし いのちさへ{\fs40}\N相思難從願 不惜下黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:17.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一張大山牌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.57,0:11:29.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惠夢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.90,0:11:34.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搶那個一字決牌的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.64,0:11:36.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圍手也被攻破了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:39.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的全身都在說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.02,0:11:44.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她會成為女王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.09,0:11:54.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然成不成為女王無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.37,0:11:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是要在這裡擊垮她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻破了圍手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.49,0:12:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能快速搶到自己擅長的牌的人有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.90,0:12:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正能分出勝負的是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.03,0:12:25.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克服自己的弱點 而不是發揮自己的強項
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.56,0:12:29.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙 到底多努力練習啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說 你的圍手太爛了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:36.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像這樣 要說幾次你才明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.27,0:12:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要以為不擅長的牌就這樣放著不管也能成為女王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.94,0:12:47.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.42,0:12:51.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽清楚 再出擊 這風格更適合綾瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.88,0:12:52.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我陪你練習
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.51,0:13:01.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做到了哦 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.67,0:13:04.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做到了哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.73,0:13:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擊垮你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:13.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走向
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要轉過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:17.50,comments_h,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\frz352.9\pos(114,228)}卡嚓卡嚓卡嚓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:17.50,comments_h,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(637,565)\fad(200,0)}靜音模式狂拍中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.91,0:13:24.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\an8}みよしのの  やまのあきかぜ{\fs40}\N故國秋風起 蕭蕭吉野山
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.71,0:13:21.21,comments_h,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\frz352.9\pos(104,216)}卡嚓卡嚓卡嚓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.71,0:13:21.21,comments_h,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(637,565)}靜音模式狂拍中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.83,0:13:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搶到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守住了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.03,0:13:26.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.04,0:13:28.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.75,0:13:32.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.77,0:13:36.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.72,0:13:38.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法連取
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惠夢碳說了「好」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惠夢碳沒有說「好了 再一張」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.48,0:13:55.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高水準的拉鋸戰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.00,0:13:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真意外
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.45,0:14:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺很敏銳 更重要的是視野很廣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:01.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有漏掉的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.48,0:14:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎麼搶都很冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.96,0:14:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要送牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.83,0:14:12.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才送出的大山牌被送還回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.27,0:14:15.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真…真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.04,0:14:18.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個孩子…絕對也是S
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.14,0:14:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\an8}あさぼらけ うぢのかはぎり たえだえに{\fs40}\N宇治臨拂曉 河灘冷霧中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被送過來的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.99,0:14:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對敵陣的牌用很低很低的圍手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.23,0:14:30.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被擺了一道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圍手被攻破時的對策自然是考慮過的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.94,0:14:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與女王對戰作為前提有練習過 和大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.15,0:14:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然女王什麼的無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.22,0:14:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果我不能獲勝的話 大家就不會開心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.13,0:14:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要在這裡 將你擊敗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.38,0:14:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變得認真了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.54,0:14:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好強
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.54,0:15:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大山牌 我還不夠成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.69,0:15:02.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,形勢嚴峻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.20,0:15:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我也注意到了一些事 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像來這邊看比賽的人變多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.09,0:15:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明石女子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:28.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本以為是只有逢坂惠夢一枝獨秀的隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.79,0:15:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟第一次和女校比賽 害我還稍微有些興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36}ながからむ{\r}\N但願情長久
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.65,0:15:38.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是好強啊 就跟男人一樣強大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.61,0:15:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的動力是逢坂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.85,0:15:45.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是其他的孩子們也確確實實的在積蓄著力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.62,0:15:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以女王為目標的逢坂的練習對手就是這麼一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.97,0:15:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有動機的話就能變得如此強大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.94,0:15:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的明石女子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.65,0:16:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是為了逢坂而變強的隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.83,0:16:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍不住要流淚了 這就是青春啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.12,0:16:11.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惠夢 都不出聲加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:14.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女生 有那麼強嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.37,0:16:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36}あらしふく{\r}\N颯颯飄紅葉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.02,0:16:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢了一點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.34,0:16:25.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要更準確 更準確一點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.95,0:16:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那1毫米
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.24,0:16:32.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.73,0:16:34.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那張牌的邊緣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.36,0:16:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36}つきみれば{\r}\N舉目望明月
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.58,0:16:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.14,0:16:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那種瞄準牌邊緣快速搶牌的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.68,0:16:57.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是逢坂出手更快 卻被趕超了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.68,0:16:59.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.41,0:17:04.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惠夢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.37,0:17:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就像是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.35,0:17:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要快速搶牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒有人對我說那句話時的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.90,0:17:37.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36}わがみひとつの  あきにはあらねど{\r}\N秋光來萬里 豈獨照一人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:48.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36}やすらはで{\r}\N若信君難到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.93,0:17:50.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36}あひみての{\r}\N自赴佳期後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.22,0:17:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連取達成了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:54.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有很華麗地搶牌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:56.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是卻確確實實做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.35,0:17:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差距…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.19,0:18:04.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差距…幾乎沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 一張 一張張地拿下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.23,0:18:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聲音太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.80,0:18:24.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪我不習慣大喊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.32,0:18:27.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36}ありあけの{\r}\N仰看無情月
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.62,0:18:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空牌也搶得這麼兇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.10,0:18:38.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟男生沒差別…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.11,0:18:38.65,comments_h,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(998,92)\frz355.4\c&HE06442&\3c&HF1F1F1&}怎麼跟男人似的…！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.56,0:18:40.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惠夢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.15,0:18:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惠夢在想什麼 我現在還搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.00,0:18:45.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定根本不在乎女王寶座
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.37,0:18:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是希望大家一起玩得高興
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.70,0:18:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.67,0:18:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惠夢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.05,0:18:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會先贏一局
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.12,0:18:56.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你慢慢來也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:19:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不懂惠夢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.54,0:19:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女王…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.80,0:19:05.05,comments_v,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz251.1\pos(1092,204)\fad(100,0)\c&HB5412B&}恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.55,0:19:05.05,comments_v,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\c&HB5412B&\frz290.5\pos(318,234)}好強
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.30,0:19:05.05,comments_v,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\c&HB5412B&\frz313.1\pos(108,562)}糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.75,0:19:05.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怖 好強 糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.76,0:19:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今年會參加女王戰預賽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:10.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變強…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.89,0:19:14.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漸漸變強 這怎會叫人不欣喜若狂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惠夢碳 你其實是個善良的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想讓大家高興 想回應大家的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.10,0:19:27.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這心情 正是你的努力之源
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.45,0:19:28.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都一清二楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.99,0:19:31.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.53,0:19:35.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更想看到一心求勝的你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.29,0:19:40.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36}こぬひとを{\r}\N思君終不見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:41.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間幾乎同時
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這是己陣的牌 所以算我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.70,0:19:45.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.46,0:19:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我搶到的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:50.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的才對 是我搶到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是幾乎同時碰到牌 牌又在我的陣地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:58.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我比你更快 我親眼看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.44,0:20:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這牌…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.53,0:20:02.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.20,0:20:01.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}惠夢她…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.69,0:20:04.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我更快一些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.98,0:20:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在爭牌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.30,0:20:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.55,0:20:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爭辯和被爭辯都超不擅長…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.58,0:20:16.33,comments_v,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz257.5\fad(130,0)\pos(646,346)}果然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.68,0:20:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夕 別說傻話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.25,0:20:21.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶領大家的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.52,0:20:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓大家都高興的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.02,0:20:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要挑戰女王的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.90,0:20:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼是你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.45,0:20:31.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.40,0:20:39.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不認識的惠夢 出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.95,0:20:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爭牌雖然輸了 但算是還了剛才讓我牌的債
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.89,0:20:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就好 綾瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.88,0:20:51.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回歸平時的千早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.47,0:20:56.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.05,0:20:59.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從現在開始進攻吧 瑞澤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.58,0:21:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.81,0:21:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 一張…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.83,0:21:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一張張地拿下來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.15,0:21:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.95,0:21:11.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在看這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.56,0:21:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩校勢均力敵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.57,0:21:18.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空氣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.63,0:21:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人的氣壓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.14,0:21:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在相互衝撞
